header.gameNote: IVY LEAGUE TOURNAMENT PRES. BY TIAA - FINAL

videos.description: Danilo Djuricic knocks down a deep 3-pointer from the top of the key to pull Harvard within 3 of Yale.
videos.headline: Djuricic nails big 3 for Harvard

videos.description:
Harvard's 
Noah Kirkwood picks the pocket of Yale's Miye Oni and runs the floor to throw down a two-handed jam on the other end.
videos.headline: Kirkwood steals and slams it home

videos.description: Alex Copeland misses the contested jumper, but Trey Phills flies in for the nasty putback dunk.
videos.headline: Phills hammers down putback dunk

videos.description: Yale defeats Harvard 97-85 to win the Ivy League tournament title and a berth into the NCAA tournament.
videos.headline: Yale wins Ivy League, earns NCCA tournament berth
